pageProduct.description:

General Information

Vita Bubs Probiotics for Baby contains 5 billion probiotics from 7 probiotic strains to support a healthy digestive system, promote the growth of good gut bacteria and support the immune system to fight illness.


Vita Bubs is dedicated to children's nutrition. The Vita Bubs range is based on scientific evidence and is proudly Australian Owned and Made.

Suitable For: 6 - 36 months

Size: 28 x 1g sachets

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each 1g sachets contains:
Total Probiotic Bacteria 5.0 Billion CFU
Lactobacillus paracasei 1.6 Billion CFU
Lactobacillus fermentum 1.6 Billion CFU
Lactobacillus rhamnosus 1.6 Billion CFU
Bifidobacterium longum 100 Million CFU
Lactobacillus acidophilus 100 Million CFU
Lactobacillus helveticus 7.5 Million CFU
Streptococcus thermophilus 7.5 Million CFU

Contains: Contains Lactose, soya beans, sugars from fructooligosaccharide.

Allergen Contains: Lactose| Soybean

Directions

Infants 6months+: 1 sachet daily, or as directed by a healthcare professional. Add powder to small amount of cold or lukewarm water, milk or food. Once fully dissolved, consume immediately.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25C in a dry place away from direct sunlight. Use within 28 days after opening.
